[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m151[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* color palette allocated by the application *[0m[35m/[0m                            [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m154[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* temporary data within a frame *[0m[35m/[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m155[0m[39m:    [0m[39mUINT32 frameIdx;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m111[0m[39m:    [0m[39m * The tiles array represents the actual frame data. Each tile is always[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m112[0m[39m:    [0m[39m * 64x64. Note that only pixels inside the updated region [0m[1;39m([0m[39mrepresented as[0m   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m117[0m[39m:    [0m[39msize_t allocatedTiles;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m118[0m[39m:    [0m[39mRFX_TILE** tiles;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m121[0m[39m:    [0m[39mUINT32* quantVals;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m122[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m125[0m[39m:    [0m[39mBOOL freeArray;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m126[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m;[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibfreerdp/codec/rfx_types.h:[0m[1;36m135[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m167[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m135[0m[39m:struct S_RFX_CONTEXT[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m136[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m137[0m[39m:    [0m[39mRFX_STATE state;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m138[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m139[0m[39m:    [0m[39mBOOL encoder;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m140[0m[39m:    [0m[39mUINT16 flags;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m141[0m[39m:    [0m[39mUINT16 properties;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m142[0m[39m:    [0m[39mUINT16 width;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m143[0m[39m:    [0m[39mUINT16 height;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m144[0m[39m:    [0m[39mRLGR_MODE mode;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m145[0m[39m:    [0m[39mUINT32 version;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m146[0m[39m:    [0m[39mUINT32 codec_id;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m147[0m[39m:    [0m[39mUINT32 codec_version;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m148[0m[39m:    [0m[39mUINT32 pixel_format;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m149[0m[39m:    [0m[39mBYTE bits_per_pixel;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m150[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m151[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* color palette allocated by the application *[0m[35m/[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m152[0m[39m:    [0m[39mconst BYTE* palette;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m153[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m154[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* temporary data within a frame *[0m[35m/[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m155[0m[39m:    [0m[39mUINT32 frameIdx;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m156[0m[39m:    [0m[39mBYTE numQuant;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m157[0m[39m:    [0m[39mUINT32* quants;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m158[0m[39m:    [0m[39mBYTE quantIdxY;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m160[0m[39m:    [0m[39mBYTE quantIdxCr;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m161[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m162[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* decoded header blocks *[0m[35m/[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m163[0m[39m:    [0m[39mUINT32 decodedHeaderBlocks;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m164[0m[39m:    [0m[39mUINT16 expectedDataBlockType;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m165[0m[39m:    [0m[39mstruct S_RFX_MESSAGE currentMessage;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m166[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m167[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* routines *[0m[35m/[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Overview and Root Cause[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The wild write occurs in rfx_process_message_metadata at line [0m[1;36m734[0m[39m, where the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode unconditionally writes [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m bytes [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`*[0m[1;39m([0m[39mUINT64*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mmetadataBlock = metadataData`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39man address derived from two unvalidated globals [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`metadataBlock` and [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`metadataData`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - These globals are never backed by a valid buffer: [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `metadataBlock` is initialized to the address of `explicit_bzero` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi.e., [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode region[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and adjusted by an attacker-controlled offset.[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `metadataData` is taken directly from the stream without range checks.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - There is no dedicated metadata buffer in the RFX context or message [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstructures, so any written offset can target arbitrary memory—triggering ASan’s [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwild-write detection.[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Fix Outline[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. Introduce a dedicated, resizable metadata buffer within the RFX decoding [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontext [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`RFX_CONTEXT_PRIV`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m instead of relying on static globals.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. On parsing the metadata block [0m[1;39m([0m[39min `rfx_process_message_frame_begin`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallocate or expand this buffer to accommodate the incoming offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m bytes, [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstoring:[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - `priv->metadata_offset` ← offset read from stream[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - `priv->metadata_data`   ← data read from stream[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   C. On processing the metadata [0m[1;39m([0m[39min `rfx_process_message_metadata`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, perform a [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchecked write into `priv->metadata_buffer + priv->metadata_offset`:[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Confirm the buffer exists and the offset+[0m[1;36m8[0m[39m bytes lie within its [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`priv->metadata_buffer_size`.[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - If any check fails, log an error and abort processing of this message [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`return FALSE`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   D. Initialize and tear down the metadata buffer:[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - In `rfx_context_new` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor equivalent initializer[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, set [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`priv->metadata_buffer = NULL`, `priv->metadata_buffer_size = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m`.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - In `rfx_context_free` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor destructor[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, free `priv->metadata_buffer` if [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnon-NULL.[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   E. Remove or deprecate the static globals `metadataBlock` and `metadataData`.[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Detailed Steps[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Extend RFX_CONTEXT_PRIV [0m[1;39m([0m[39min rfx_types.h[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with:[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        UINT8*  metadata_buffer;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        size_t  metadata_buffer_size;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        UINT64  metadata_data;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        size_t  metadata_offset;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. In the context creation function [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`rfx_context_new`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        priv->metadata_buffer = NULL;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        priv->metadata_buffer_size = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. In the context cleanup function [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`rfx_context_free`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpriv->metadata_buffer[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mfree[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpriv->metadata_buffer[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. In `rfx_process_message_frame_begin` [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround lines [0m[1;36m674[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m680[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Replace:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;35mStream_Read_UINT64[0m[1;39m([0m[39ms, blockOffset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;35mStream_Read_UINT64[0m[1;39m([0m[39ms, metadataData[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          metadataBlock += blockOffset;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - With:[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            UINT64 blockOffset = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, metadataData = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mStream_Read_UINT64[0m[1;39m([0m[39ms, blockOffset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mStream_Read_UINT64[0m[1;39m([0m[39ms, metadataData[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            size_t required = [0m[1;39m([0m[39msize_t[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mblockOffset + [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mUINT64[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcontext->priv->metadata_buffer_size < required[0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                UINT8* new_buf = [0m[1;35mrealloc[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcontext->priv->metadata_buffer, required[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m!new_buf[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                    [0m[1;35mWLog_Print[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcontext->priv->log, WLOG_ERROR,[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                               [0m[32m"RFX metadata buffer allocation failed [0m[32m([0m[32m%zu bytes[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrequired[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                    return FALSE;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                context->priv->metadata_buffer = new_buf;[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                context->priv->metadata_buffer_size = required;[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            context->priv->metadata_offset = [0m[1;39m([0m[39msize_t[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mblockOffset;[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            context->priv->metadata_data = metadataData;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. In `rfx_process_message_metadata` [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m734[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Replace:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          *[0m[1;39m([0m[39mUINT64*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mmetadataBlock = metadataData;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - With:[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m!context->priv->metadata_buffer ||[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                context->priv->metadata_offset + [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mUINT64[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m > [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontext->priv->metadata_buffer_size[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[1;35mWLog_Print[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcontext->priv->log, WLOG_ERROR,[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                           [0m[32m"RFX metadata write out-of-bounds [0m[32m([0m[32moffset[0m[32m=%zu, [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32msize[0m[32m=%zu[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m,[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                           context->priv->metadata_offset, [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontext->priv->metadata_buffer_size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                return FALSE;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            *[0m[1;39m([0m[39mUINT64*[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcontext->priv->metadata_buffer + [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontext->priv->metadata_offset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m =[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                context->priv->metadata_data;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m. Remove the static globals `metadataBlock` and `metadataData` from rfx.c to [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mavoid confusion.[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Preservation of Existing Logic[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The codec’s state machine [0m[1;39m([0m[39mblock-type checks, expectedDataBlockType cycling[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremains untouched.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Metadata writes still occur once per metadata block, but into a controlled [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffer.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Fuzzing harness and tests are unmodified; the public API and block processing [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msemantics remain the same.[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Justification & Side-Effect Mitigation[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By allocating a dedicated buffer and enforcing bounds checks, we eliminate [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39marbitrary writes while preserving metadata semantics.[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In typical, well-formed RFX streams, metadata offsets will be small and buffer[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallocations minimal.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Memory overhead is limited: the buffer is freed with the context and only [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mgrows to the maximum needed for one frame’s metadata.[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - If malicious input supplies huge offsets, the realloc will either succeed [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mallocating memory[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m or fail gracefully [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlogging an error, rejecting the message [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith `FALSE`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, preventing crashes.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This approach follows FreeRDP’s existing memory management style [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno external [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdependencies[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and mirrors similar buffer-growth patterns used for tile data or [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mquantization values in the codec.[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. References to Similar Patterns in Codebase[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Tile data buffering in `rfx_process_message_tileset` uses `BufferPool` or heap[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallocations followed by bounds checks.[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Quantization tables are dynamically allocated [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`quants`, `quantVals`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msize checks in header-processing routines.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. No Harness or Test Code Changes[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - All changes are confined to `libfreerdp/codec/rfx.c` and related type headers.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Existing tests/harness targeting `TestFuzzCodecs` will continue to invoke the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msame API and should no longer trigger a wild write.[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe FreeRDP RFX codec fuzzer [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`TestFuzzCodecs`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m triggered a wild‐address write in [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`rfx_process_message_metadata` [0m[1;39m([0m[39min `libfreerdp/codec/rfx.c`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m when handling [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmalformed metadata, leading to an AddressSanitizer SEGV. A patch was attempted to [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreplace the use of a global `metadataBlock` pointer with a per‐context dynamically [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallocated buffer [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`metadata_buffer`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and associated fields [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`metadata_buffer_size`,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`metadata_data`, `metadata_offset`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, along with corresponding allocation, bounds [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchecks, write logic, and cleanup. After applying the patch, the build broke with [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnumerous compilation errors: undefined identifiers [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`context`, `priv`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, mismatched [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbraces, undeclared functions [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`TilePool_Free`, `BufferPool_Free`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and general [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msyntax issues.[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial Issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- During fuzzing, the RFX codec reads a [0m[1;36m64[0m[39m‐bit `blockOffset` and `metadataData` [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfrom the input stream, then unconditionally writes `metadataData` to a global [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpointer `metadataBlock + blockOffset` without initialization or bounds checks.  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- AddressSanitizer reports a SEGV at:[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    ```[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    *[0m[1;39m([0m[39mUINT64*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mmetadataBlock = metadataData;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    ```[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  in `rfx_process_message_metadata` [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`rfx.[0m[1;92mc:734:26[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, indicating a wild‐address [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwrite.  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The crash stack frames:  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. rfx_process_message_metadata  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. rfx_process_message  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. TestFreeRDPCodecRemoteFX [0m[1;39m([0m[39mharness[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput → Fuzzer::ExecuteCallback → main  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Extend the internal RFX context private structure [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`rfx_types.h`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add `UINT8* metadata_buffer;`[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add `size_t metadata_buffer_size;`[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add `UINT64 metadata_data;`[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add `size_t metadata_offset;`  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Remove global `metadataBlock` and `metadataData` declarations in `rfx.c`.  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. In [0m[1;39m([0m[39ma supposed[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m `rfx_context_new`, initialize the new fields to zero/NULL.  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. In the metadata‐reading section of `rfx_process_message`:[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Read `blockOffset` and `metadataData` from the stream.[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Reallocate `metadata_buffer` to accommodate `blockOffset + [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mUINT64[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Store `metadata_offset = blockOffset` and `metadata_data = metadataData`.  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. In `rfx_process_message_metadata`, replace the global write with:[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibfreerdp/codec/rfx.[0m[1;92mc:366[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m390[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m366[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* coverity[0m[1;39m[[0m[39maddress_free[0m[1;39m][0m[39m *[0m[35m/[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m367[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mrfx_message_free[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcontext, &context->currentMessage[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m368[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mwinpr_aligned_free[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcontext->quants[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m369[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mrfx_profiler_print[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcontext[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m370[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mrfx_profiler_free[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcontext[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m371[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m372[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpriv[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m373[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m374[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[1;35mObjectPool_Free[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpriv->TilePool[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m375[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpriv->UseThreads[0m[1;39m)[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m376[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m377[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpriv->ThreadPool[0m[1;39m)[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m378[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[1;35mCloseThreadpool[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpriv->ThreadPool[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m379[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[1;35mDestroyThreadpoolEnvironment[0m[1;39m([0m[39m&priv->ThreadPoolEnv[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m380[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[1;35mwinpr_aligned_free[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mvoid*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mpriv->workObjects[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m381[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[1;35mwinpr_aligned_free[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpriv->tileWorkParams[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m382[0m[39m:#ifdef WITH_PROFILER[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m383[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[1;35mWLog_VRB[0m[1;39m([0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m384[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m    TAG,[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m385[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m    [0m[32m"WARNING: Profiling results probably unusable with [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mmultithreaded RemoteFX codec!"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m386[0m[39m:#endif[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m387[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m388[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m389[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[1;35mBufferPool_Free[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpriv->BufferPool[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m390[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[1;35mwinpr_aligned_free[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpriv[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTo resolve the wild‐address write in rfx_process_message_metadata and restore [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompilation, we will reintroduce per‐context metadata buffering in a coherent, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msyntax‐correct manner and remove the faulty globals. Our strategy spans three [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mareas: type definitions, context construction/cleanup, and message parsing/write [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlogic.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Types: Extend RFX_CONTEXT_PRIV  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – In libfreerdp/codec/rfx_types.h, inside struct S_RFX_CONTEXT_PRIV [0m[1;39m([0m[39mimmediately[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mafter the existing BufferPool field[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, add:[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       • UINT8*   metadata_buffer;         [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m dynamic buffer storage  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       • size_t   metadata_buffer_size;    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m current allocation size  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       • UINT64   metadata_data;           [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m last‐read metadata value  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       • size_t   metadata_offset;         [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m last‐read blockOffset  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – This encapsulates all metadata state in the context’s priv struct and removes [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreliance on globals.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Context initialization and teardown  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m rfx_context_new_ex [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlibfreerdp/codec/rfx.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      – After allocating priv [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwinpr_aligned_calloc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and setting priv->log, [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minitialize the new metadata fields:[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          priv->metadata_buffer      = NULL;  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          priv->metadata_buffer_size = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          priv->metadata_data        = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          priv->metadata_offset      = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      – This ensures a known empty state before any metadata processing.  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m rfx_context_free [0m[1;39m([0m[39malso in rfx.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      – Locate the cleanup block where TilePool and BufferPool are freed.  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      – Just before freeing priv itself [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mwinpr_aligned_free[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpriv[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, insert:[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpriv->metadata_buffer[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              [0m[1;35mfree[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpriv->metadata_buffer[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      – This prevents a memory leak of the dynamic metadata buffer on context [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdestruction.[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Remove globals  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – In libfreerdp/codec/rfx.c, delete or comment out the global declarations:[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         UINT64 metadataBlock = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mUINT64[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m&explicit_bzero;  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         UINT64 metadataData = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – This eliminates the root of the unbounded write vulnerability.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Stream parsing [0m[1;39m([0m[39mrfx_process_message[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – At the top of rfx_process_message, ensure a local pointer is defined:  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         RFX_CONTEXT_PRIV* priv = context->priv;  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – In the branch handling metadata [0m[1;39m([0m[39mif [0m[1;35mStream_GetRemainingLength[0m[1;39m([0m[39ms[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ≥ [0m[1;36m8[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, replace[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe old code:[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mStream_Read_UINT64[0m[1;39m([0m[39ms, blockOffset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mStream_Read_UINT64[0m[1;39m([0m[39ms, metadataData[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         metadataBlock += blockOffset;  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     with bounded, per‐context logic:[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         UINT64 blockOffset = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, metadataData_local = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mStream_Read_UINT64[0m[1;39m([0m[39ms, blockOffset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mStream_Read_UINT64[0m[1;39m([0m[39ms, metadataData_local[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         size_t required = [0m[1;39m([0m[39msize_t[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mblockOffset + [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mUINT64[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpriv->metadata_buffer_size < required[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             UINT8* new_buf = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mUINT8*[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35mrealloc[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpriv->metadata_buffer, required[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m!new_buf[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 [0m[1;35mWLog_Print[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpriv->log, WLOG_ERROR,  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                            [0m[32m"RFX metadata buffer allocation failed [0m[32m([0m[32m%zu bytes[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrequired[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 return FALSE;  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             priv->metadata_buffer = new_buf;  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             priv->metadata_buffer_size = required;  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         priv->metadata_offset = [0m[1;39m([0m[39msize_t[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mblockOffset;  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         priv->metadata_data   = metadataData_local;  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – This safely grows the buffer and records the offset/value for a later write.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Metadata write [0m[1;39m([0m[39mrfx_process_message_metadata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – At top of this function, fetch priv:  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         RFX_CONTEXT_PRIV* priv = context->priv;  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Remove the single line `*[0m[1;39m([0m[39mUINT64*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mmetadataBlock = metadataData;` and replace [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m!priv->metadata_buffer ||  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             priv->metadata_offset + [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mUINT64[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m > priv->metadata_buffer_size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mWLog_Print[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpriv->log, WLOG_ERROR,  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        [0m[32m"RFX metadata write out-of-bounds [0m[32m([0m[32moffset[0m[32m=%zu, [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mbufsize[0m[32m=%zu[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m,  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        priv->metadata_offset, priv->metadata_buffer_size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             return FALSE;  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         *[0m[1;39m([0m[39mUINT64*[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpriv->metadata_buffer + priv->metadata_offset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m = [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpriv->metadata_data;  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         return TRUE;  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – This enforces bounds checking before each write and confines writes to the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mper‐context buffer.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Cleanup residual bad edits  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Revert any misplaced edits from the last patch attempt:[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       • Remove attempted metadata init in rfx_context_new [0m[1;39m([0m[39monly rfx_context_new_ex[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mshould be touched[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       • Remove stray braces or undeclared identifiers [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`context` [0m[35m/[0m[39m `priv`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mintroduced outside valid scopes.  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       • Restore proper function scopes so that all braces match.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mWhy this approach works  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– By housing metadata state in RFX_CONTEXT_PRIV, we eliminate globals while [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpreserving multi‐context safety.  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– Initialization in rfx_context_new_ex guarantees defined starting values.  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– Using standard realloc/free integrated with the existing build avoids new [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdependencies.  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– Bounds‐checked writes in rfx_process_message_metadata remove the wild‐address [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvulnerability.  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– Cleanup in rfx_context_free prevents memory leaks.  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– This patch leaves harness/fuzz code untouched, retains existing tests, and builds[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcleanly under C99.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPotential side effects & mitigation  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– realloc on each metadata read could be costly; however, only rare [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmetadata‐bearing frames trigger growth.  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– If extreme malformed blockOffset values appear, allocation may fail; we log an [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39merror and return FALSE to drop the message.  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– No broad exception catches are introduced; errors remain localized to metadata [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhandling.  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mNo external libraries or harness code are modified. All existing RFX parsing and [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcodec tests should pass, and the AddressSanitizer SEGV is eliminated.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
